data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER!! ***  Seller is offering $10,000 in concessions for closing cost or rate buy down. ***Home could be a VA Assumption with qualified buyer. If you are looking for that perfect balance between country and city living in a resort style community this move in ready home is for you. This exceptional residence showcases a rare  1.5 story floor plan that will fall in love with. Nestled in a highly desired Redbird Ranch  neighborhood, this property blends sophistication and comfort seamlessly. The main level boasts two spacious living areas, ideal for entertaining. There are two bedrooms in the front of the home as well as a full bath. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream come true with gleaming kitchen appliances and ample cabinet and pantry storage. This space is perfect for hosting parties or hanging out with loved ones. Unwind in the Master retreat while enjoying a glass of wine relaxing in the garden tub with the softness of the water softener and no worries about hard water stains. You will also find a master closet you could get lost in.  Ascend to the second level and discover a flexible loft area ready for your imagination. Whether you envision a game room, a cozy reading nook, or a private fitness area, this space is yours to customize and make your own. Just off of the loft area you will find a private bedroom and bathroom.  This home features a completely finished out garage as well as UV Air Purifier on the HVAC to help you breath easier. In this home you will be less than a mile to highway 211 that gets you downtown for dinner or shopping. Bonus feature if you run out of milk or wine you are a few minutes away from Texas favorite grocery stores HEB.   This community has so much to offer like relaxing in any of the TWO huge community pools, play some tennis/pickle ball or basketball. Or if you want to get some steps in you are steps away from the communities amazing hiking/biking trails.   Do not miss out on living amongst amazing people in the perfect home.  Schedule a showing today and let your imagination take flight!  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7HgVvx7j9-o
